objectives.en:
1) to support student's improvement to be a teacher by creating continuous opportunities to associate theoretical knowledge with teacher's activities in an educational institution;
2) to develop skills and habit to reflect other teachers' and students' activities in order to support their own development as a teacher;
3) to support defining him/herself as a member of the school personnel, who collaborates according to the type of the educational institution with students, different teachers, administration, support specialists and/or parents;

learning_outcomes.en:
1) is able to analyze his/her competence, skills and needs in order to plan his/her further actions;
2) acquires according to the educational institution type primary skills to work together with colleagues, children and/or parents;
3) identifies his/herself as a teacher and understands responsibilities and obligations in different situations that derive from that role;

learning_outcomes.et:
Üliõpilane
1)	märkab I kooliastmele sobivaid  õpetamismeetodeid, kirjeldab (õpipäevikus) ja seostab neid teooriaga; 
2)	tegutseb abiõpetaja rollis,  kavandab ja analüüsib juhendaja abiga õppetööd ;
3)	viib läbi esimesed proovitunnid ja analüüsib neid.
